SourcePackages:
- sailfishsilica-qt5 >= 1.1.86.1

Prefix: /usr/lib/qt5/qml/Sailfish/Silica/private
DisplayName: Check mark for remorse timer [SFOS 3.x]
PackageName: sfos-patch-remorse-check-mark
Category: Silica

Keywords:
- Patch
- Remorse
- Design

Maintainer: ichthyosaurus
Summary: [obsolete] Change the remorse timer 'X' icon to a check mark
Description:
- **This patch is obsolete since SFOS 4.x, as the 'X' icon has been removed.**
-
- This patch keeps the current remorse timer design but changes the 'X' icon to a check mark.
-
- Another patch is available [here](https://openrepos.net/content/ichthyosaurus/patch-remove-icon-remorse-timer)
- that removes the icon completely.

DiscussionLink: https://forum.sailfishos.org/t/patches-by-ichthyosaurus
